      "span_text": "In situ heating experiments were carried out at the Austrian SAXS beamline at Elettra synchrotron Trieste, Italy, with a fixed energy of 8.00 keV.  For this experiment, a Pilatus3 1 M detector (Dectris, Switzerland) was used, which gave access to a q-range from 0.01−0.65 Å −1"
